Interface PlayerProvider

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
BukkitPlayerProvider, FabricPlayerProvider, FoliaPlayerProvider, SpongePlayerProvider
public interface PlayerProvider extends net.tnemc.menu.core.compatibility.MenuPlayer
A class that acts as a bridge between various player objects on different server software providers.
